-r-na/overview,,https://vortexgallery.moe/info#JJBAASBR,0,0,0,3,None,b09af56b,0,0 Hours,Steam,NA,AaronCurryDish,-8,-8,2024-10-11T23:00:00.000Z,PST,aaroncurry,JoJo's Bizarre Adventure: All Star Battle R,https://v5.airtableusercontent.com/v3/u/32/32/1725955200000/28TOOTFnpclWMOF9hlq7iQ/C8DUwxHwypPskZa1d35ujVMSq6vxn2gDYSov9NOg0mzfw-CdxQxz5qhZ4Sy800Ib9k3NSzxKfY6p9HzDPGD2dgCoN8WUSjTm0RGOhjmVJrsjClHUrJUyM5ltVtZyQ8EKFRigUD9tUPATiUTh9voVMg/TKJ7ksi18YqOvyMEgdgI0nYUFXYSAiojEdUg5QCntr4,https://hook.us1.make.com/u95rhpxkvbdebwkxjuko85hdocglukl7?type=logo&recordID=recDk1gxF9KU3GMEV,JJBA ASBR,https://matcherino.com/tournaments/116766,recxR5B8uJW07jZXw,True,"3/5 Games for Losers Finals, 3/5 Games for Winners Finals, 3/5 Games for Grand Finals",,Winner must keep character. Loser may switch.,recX3d0togyUPvDAT,Aaron Curry,,"Parsec, download from https://parsec.app/ and set up an account","- Must be in the Discord.

- Timer: 99 seconds

- Rounds: 3

- Hazards: OFF

- Assists: ON

- Matches Format: Initially, all matches are Best of 3 (FT2). As we progress to Winners Finals, Losers Finals, and Grand Finals, the format shifts to Best of 5 (FT3).

- Stage Selection: We encourage Random Select for Stages; however, if both players mutually agree on a specific map, they are free to choose it.

- Reselection: Losers are allowed to switch Character, Assist, and Map; winners must stick with their choices.

- Connection: Wired ethernet only.

- ""North America Only"": Even though it says North America Only, other players that are not from North America can join and participate in the tournament. However, they are not allowed to host their computer on Parsec nor do Netplay; they can only join NA players hosting their computers or joining a Shadow.

- Game Ownership: It is recommended that you own JoJo's All-Star Battle R; however, all you really need is Parsec.

