_Rules-Glitches=This%20is%20a%20rare%20but%20known%20bug%20which%20can%20occur%20with%20toss-ups%20on%20certain%20characters%2C%20most%20notably%20when%20Steve%20Miller%20is%20trying%20to%20catch%20the%20disc.%20These%20points%20are%20honored%20in%20tournament%20as%20the%20bug%20is%20very%20hard%20to%20reproduce%20and%20there%20is%20no%20easy%20way%20to%20discount%20these%20points%20without%20completely%20disrupting%20the%20match.%0A%0AIn%20the%20event%20that%20it%20happens%2C%20restart%20the%20match%20and%20try%20to%20replicate%20the%20score%20before%20the%20glitch.%20If%20this%20cannot%20be%20done%2C%20contact%20the%20TO%2FBracket%20Runners.%20&prefill_Rules-Chara%20Change=Winner%20must%20keep%20character.%20Loser%20may%20switch.&prefill_Rules-Game%20Settings=-%20First%20to%202%20Wins%2C%20%20TOP%204%20FIRST%20TO%203.%20%0A-%20First%20stage%20is%20BEACH.%20Loser%20counterpicks%20stage.%20%0A-%20No%20Characters%20are%20banned.%20%0A-%20Standard%20Settings%20apply%20%28Set%20Count%20%3D%202%2C%20Winning%20Point%20%20%3D%2012%2C%20Timer%20%3D%2099%29%0A-%20%20In%20case%20of%20Draw%20both%20players%20enter%20the%20same%20stage%20with%20same%20characters%20and%20first%20score%20wins%20the%20game%20%28aka%20Extended%20Sudden%20Death%29%0A-%20DSR%20is%20in%20play%3A%20You%20may%20not%20select%20a%20stage%20you%20have%20previously%20won%20on%20in%20the%20same%20set.%20%0A-%20PLEASE%20ENSURE%20YOU%20ARE%20USING%20A%20WIRED%20CONNECTION.%20Wi-Fi%20connections%20are%20not%20acceptable.%20%0A-%20All%20Matches%20must%20provide%20either%20a%20fightcade%20replay%20or%20a%20video%20replay%20in%20extreme%20cases.%20If%20no%20replay%20can%20be%20provided%2C%20Staff%20reserves%20the%20right%20to%20choose%20a%20player%20to%20advance.%0A-%20In%20the%20event%20that%20a%20match%20cannot%20be%20played%20or%20a%20lobby%20cannot%20be%20formed%20between%20players%2C%20inform%20the%20TO.%20&prefill_Finals-Games%20per%20Set=3%2F5%20Games%20for%20Grand%20Finals%2C%203%2F5%20Games%20for%20Winne